<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>여의명상센터 — 한울사상 | 고요 속으로</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@200;300;400;600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    <%
    const palettes = {
      1: { bg:'#F7F5F0', text:'#1E1C18', text2:'#7A7268', accent:'#8B6840', hero:'#1A1712', heroText:'rgba(247,245,240,0.95)' },
      2: { bg:'#F5F7F4', text:'#1A221A', text2:'#5A6E5A', accent:'#4A7A47', hero:'#111A11', heroText:'rgba(245,247,244,0.95)' },
      3: { bg:'#F8F4EF', text:'#221A10', text2:'#7A6A54', accent:'#9A7040', hero:'#18120A', heroText:'rgba(248,244,239,0.95)' },
      4: { bg:'#F4F7F8', text:'#101E22', text2:'#486068', accent:'#3A7A88', hero:'#0A1416', heroText:'rgba(244,247,248,0.95)' },
      5: { bg:'#F7F5F0', text:'#1E1C18', text2:'#7A7268', accent:'#6A6050', hero:'#1A1712', heroText:'rgba(247,245,240,0.95)' },
    };
    const p = palettes[((themeId-1)%5)+1];
    %>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: <%= p.bg %>;
      --text: <%= p.text %>;
      --text2: <%= p.text2 %>;
      --accent: <%= p.accent %>;
      --hero: <%= p.hero %>;
      --hero-text: <%= p.heroText %>;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── FIXED NAV ── */
    .nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 6vw; height: 72px;
      background: transparent;
      transition: background 0.6s ease, border-bottom 0.6s ease;
    }
    .nav.solid {
      background: rgba(247,245,240,0.97);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: var(--hero-text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.6s;
    }
    .nav.solid .nav-logo { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.8rem; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.6s;
    }
    .nav.solid .nav-links a { color: var(--text2); }
    .nav.solid .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
      background: var(--hero);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    /* 배경: 방사형 그라디언트 — 중심 약간 밝음 */
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(
        ellipse 120% 80% at 50% 60%,
        rgba(139,104,64,0.18) 0%,
        rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    /* 하단 페이드 */
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 280px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--hero));
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
    }
    /* 대형 한자 — 배경 장식 */
    .hero-hanja-bg {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(14rem, 28vw, 22rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      line-height: 1;
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -52%);
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }
    /* 메인 한자 */
    .hero-hanja {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 9vw, 7rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--hero-text);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.8s 0.4s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .hero-line {
      width: 1px; height: 60px;
      background: rgba(247,245,240,0.25);
      margin: 2.4rem 0;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.8s 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .hero-ko {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.5rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--hero-text);
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.8s 1.0s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.55);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      line-height: 2;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.8s 1.3s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 5vh; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.8s 1.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .hero-scroll span {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.4);
    }
    .scroll-bar {
      width: 1px; height: 52px;
      background: rgba(247,245,240,0.2);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .scroll-bar::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: -100%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: rgba(247,245,240,0.7);
      animation: scrollDrop 2.2s 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scrollDrop { 0%{top:-100%} 100%{top:200%} }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform: none; }
    }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .section-divider {
      width: 1px; height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── INTRO ── */
    .intro {
      padding: 14vh 6vw 14vh;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .intro-quote {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .intro-cite {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 2.4rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text2);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    /* ── PHILOSOPHY ── */
    .phil-section {
      padding: 12vh 0;
      background: var(--hero);
    }
    .phil-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 6vw;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .phil-item {
      padding: 8vh 4vw;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      position: relative;
    }
    .phil-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .phil-hanja {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      line-height: 1;
      display: block;
    }
    .phil-divider {
      width: 28px; height: 1px;
      background: var(--accent);
      margin: 2rem auto;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .phil-ko {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    /* ── SPACER SECTION (여백 섹션) ── */
    .spacer-section {
      padding: 18vh 6vw;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .spacer-number {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(6rem, 15vw, 12rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(30,28,24,0.05);
      line-height: 1;
      user-select: none;
    }

    /* ── ABOUT ── */
    .about {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14vh 6vw;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 8vw;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .about-label {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      color: var(--text2);
      padding-top: 6px;
    }
    .about-body {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 2.4;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .about-accent {
      display: block; margin-top: 3rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ── PROGRAMS ── */
    .programs {
      padding: 14vh 6vw;
      background: var(--hero);
    }
    .programs-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10vh;
    }
    .programs-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .programs-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .prog-list {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
    }
    .prog-item {
      padding: 6vh 3.5vw;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .prog-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .prog-num {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      display: block; margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .prog-name {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.6vw, 1.15rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .prog-desc {
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    /* ── SCHEDULE ── */
    .schedule {
      max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14vh 6vw;
    }
    .sch-header {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8vh;
    }
    .sch-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: var(--text2);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .sch-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .sch-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .sch-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
      padding: 2.8vh 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .sch-date {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .sch-name {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .sch-place {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text2);
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* ── FULLSCREEN QUOTE ── */
    .quote-full {
      min-height: 78vh;
      background: var(--hero);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 12vh 8vw;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .quote-full-inner {
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .qf-mark {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 0.5;
      opacity: 0.6;
      display: block; margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .qf-text {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.4vw, 1.7rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.88);
      line-height: 2.2;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    }
    .qf-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 5rem;
      padding: 1rem 3.5rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(247,245,240,0.25);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    .qf-cta:hover {
      border-color: rgba(247,245,240,0.7);
      color: rgba(247,245,240,0.95);
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 10vh 6vw 6vh;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5vw;
    }
    .footer-brand h3 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .footer-brand p {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text2);
      line-height: 2.2; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      color: var(--text2);
      margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }
    .footer-col a {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      line-height: 2.4; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 5vh auto 0;
      padding-top: 3vh;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-bottom p {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: var(--text2); letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    /* ── THEME BADGE ── */
    .theme-badge {
      position: fixed; bottom: 14px; right: 14px; z-index: 9999;
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 3px; max-width: 260px; justify-content: flex-end;
    }
    .theme-badge a {
      display: inline-block; padding: 2px 6px;
      font-size: 9px; border-radius: 2px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .theme-badge a.active, .theme-badge a:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }

    /* ── REVEAL ── */
    .reveal { opacity:0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease; }
    .reveal.vis { opacity:1; transform: none; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .prog-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .prog-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
      .phil-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .phil-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .sch-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- THEME BADGE -->
<nav class="theme-badge">
  <% for(let i=1;i<=20;i++){ %><a href="/siann-23/<%= i %>" class="<%= themeId==i?'active':'' %>">T<%= i %></a><% } %>
</nav>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav" id="mainNav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">여의명상센터</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#about">센터소개</a>
    <a href="#philosophy">한울사상</a>
    <a href="#programs">수련프로그램</a>
    <a href="#schedule">일정</a>
    <a href="http://211.104.37.65:4200" target="_blank">법문아카이브</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ① HERO — 100vh, 순수 CSS 배경, 대형 한자 靜 -->
<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-hanja-bg" aria-hidden="true">靜</span>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-hanja">靜</span>
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
    <span class="hero-ko">여의명상센터</span>
    <p class="hero-sub">한울사상 · 韓蔚思想<br>하늘의 뜻으로 사는 삶</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>SCROLL</span>
    <div class="scroll-bar"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ② INTRO QUOTE -->
<div class="intro reveal" id="about">
  <p class="intro-quote">
    "나비가 될 번데기는<br>오늘도 껍질을 깨는 중이다"
  </p>
  <cite class="intro-cite">— 한울사상 법문</cite>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- ③ PHILOSOPHY — 다크 섹션, 한자 3개 -->
<section class="phil-section" id="philosophy">
  <div class="phil-grid">
    <div class="phil-item reveal">
      <span class="phil-hanja">道</span>
      <div class="phil-divider"></div>
      <span class="phil-ko">우주도리</span>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-item reveal">
      <span class="phil-hanja">靈</span>
      <div class="phil-divider"></div>
      <span class="phil-ko">영적진화</span>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-item reveal">
      <span class="phil-hanja">責</span>
      <div class="phil-divider"></div>
      <span class="phil-ko">세상책임</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--hero), var(--accent), var(--bg)); height: 120px; width: 1px; margin: 0 auto;"></div>

<!-- ④ ABOUT — 극도의 여백, 텍스트 최소화 -->
<section class="about">
  <div class="about-label reveal">CENTER<br>STORY</div>
  <div class="about-body reveal">
    침묵이 말하는 자리로 오세요.<br><br>
    여의명상센터는 한울사상을 바탕으로<br>
    내면의 고요함을 찾는 이들이 모이는 공간입니다.
    <span class="about-accent">서울 영등포 · 매주 토요일</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 큰 숫자 여백 장식 -->
<div class="spacer-section" aria-hidden="true">
  <span class="spacer-number">10,313</span>
</div>

<!-- ⑤ PROGRAMS — 다크 섹션 -->
<section class="programs" id="programs">
  <div class="programs-header reveal">
    <div class="programs-eyebrow">PROGRAMS</div>
    <div class="programs-title">수련 프로그램</div>
  </div>
